title: Carolyn Angus
text: Unfortunately I ordered 3 canon printer refills to take advantage of the lower individual cost about par with Kmart but when it came, very promptly ( I can't complain about the service), it does not work I have tried everything, had 2 other people check it for me. The monitor says I have plenty of ink in there but it won't print!?!? Is it because it is not canon?
